Package: democracyData
Type: Package
Title: Access and manipulate most available democracy datasets 
Version: 0.2.1
Description: Contains a number of functions to access and manipulate a large number of democracy datasets, many of historical interest. It also contains a number of functions to determine membership of a country in standard membership lists of the state system (according to Gleditsch and Ward, Correlates of War, or Polity).
Authors@R: person("Xavier", "Marquez", role=c("aut", "cre"),
  email = "marquez.x@gmail.com")
